# contract-drift.tflw тАФ DEMO-FAIL FIXTURE (M24, testFlow PLAN.md decision 102a): apiV2's
# `/contract-demo/drifted` endpoint documents a `price` field via `@ApiOkResponse` that its real
# handler never returns тАФ a realistic "schema says a field exists but the API stopped returning
# it" drift. Shows the contract matcher actually catching real drift (TFLW-GAPS.md gap #6),
# not just passing on well-behaved endpoints.
#
# Run explicitly (dot-directory, invisible to a bare `tflw run`/`tflw check`):
#   npx tflw run tests/.demo-fail/contract-drift.tflw --tag demofail

@demofail @contract
test "a drifted endpoint fails contract validation on its missing documented field"
  api GET /contract-demo/drifted
  expect status equals 200
  expect body matches schema "DriftedWidgetResponseDto" from "http://localhost:4001/openapi.json"
